    "A compact and lightweight kiwifruit picker was developed based on kiwifruit characteristics.",
    "It recognizes and locates ripe fruits and picks them by clamping and twisting.",
    "The design of the machine lays the foundation for further research in automatic sorting technology (Gao et al. 2013).",
    "Williams et al. (2019) developed a multi-armed kiwifruit harvesting device with a novel harvesting mechanism to efficiently harvest kiwifruit from the canopy.",
    "Field trials demonstrated a harvest rate of 51% with an average harvest cycle time of 5.5 s/unit, but with long wastage times and fruit losses of up to 23.4%."
